task: Available tasks for this project:
* build:           Build the project
                   deps: lint, test:unit
                   summary: Compiles the Go binary for the current platform.
* deploy:          Deploy the application
                   requires: VERSION, ENV (enum: staging, production)
                   deps: build
                   summary: Deploys the built artifact to the target environment.
* lint:            Run linters
* test:unit:       Run unit tests
                   requires: COVERAGE
